TrP = os.listdir('train/pepsi')

TeC = os.listdir('test/cocacola')
TeP = os.listdir('test/pepsi')

[1] 데이터 로딩 및 전처리¶

트레이닝 코카콜라¶

In [894]:
in_size = 32*32*3

img = []

for file in TrC:
    im = cv2.imread('train/cocacola/'+file)
    # 정규화한 1차원 배열
    # 입력 데이터 크기 : 32*32 픽셀
    im = cv2.resize(im, (32,32))  # 사이즈 조정
    im = im.reshape(-1,in_size)/255
    im = np.ravel(im)  # 1차원으로 변환
    img.append(im)
    
TrC_df=pd.DataFrame(img)
TrC_df.insert(0, '브랜드', '코카콜라')
TrC_df=TrC_df.T

train_df = pd.concat([TrC_df, TrP_df], axis=1).T
test_df = pd.concat([TeC_df, TeP_df], axis=1).T

train_df = train_df.reset_index(drop=True)
test_df = test_df.reset_index(drop=True)

    try:
        # 모델 객체 생성
        md=model()
        # 학습
        md.fit(train_input, train_target)
        # 평가
        result=md.score(test_input, test_target)
        scores.append((name, np.round(result, 3)))
    except:
        pass

n_estimators=[10,50,100,200]  # 트리 수
max_depth=[3,None]  # 트리 최대 깊이(값이 클수록 모델 복잡도 ▲)

min_samples_leaf=[2,6]  # 리프 노드에 있어야 하는 최소 샘플 수

             'max_depth':max_depth,
             'max_features':max_features,
             'min_samples_split':min_samples_split,
             'min_samples_leaf':min_samples_leaf}

[5] 모델 재 트레이닝 <- 하이퍼파라미터 적용¶

In [977]:
hgbc = HistGradientBoostingClassifier(learning_rate=0.5, max_depth=10)

log = LogisticRegression(max_iter=1000, penalty='l1', solver='saga')

gbc = GradientBoostingClassifier(learning_rate=0.5, n_estimators=1000)

sgdc = SGDClassifier(penalty='elasticnet', alpha=0.0001, loss='hinge')

svc = SVC(C=100, gamma=0.001)

rf = RandomForestClassifier(max_depth=None, max_features=0.5, min_samples_leaf=2, min_samples_split=2, n_estimators=200)
In [985]:
# 교차검증
models = [hgbc, log, gbc, sgdc, svc, rf]
model_names = ['HistGradientBoostingClassifier','LogisticRegression','GradientBoostingClassifier',
               'SGDClassifier','SVC','RandomForestClassifier']
scores3 = {}

for ind, mod in enumerate(models):
    mod.fit(train_input, train_target)
    acc = cross_val_score(mod, train_input, train_target, scoring = 'accuracy', cv=10)
    scores3[model_names[ind]] = acc
In [1042]:
# 모델 정확도에 대한 시각화
v=[]

for i in model_names:
    v.append(np.mean(scores3[i]))
    
v.sort()

idx=[2,0,5,1,4,3]
name=[]
for i in idx:
    name.append(model_names[i])
    
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 7))
plt.barh(name, v, color = 'tomato')
plt.title('Machin Learning Algorithm Accuaracy Score \n')
plt.xlabel('Accuracy Score (%)')
plt.show()
